Destructor with private specifier called private destructors.

When we want to prevent destruction of object we can make destructor private

What is use of Private Destructor ? 

Whenever we want to control the destruction of object of class we can make destructor private.
For dynamically created object if we create a function to deletes object.

If object is refferred after function call, the reference will become dangling.

When class has private destructor only dynamic type of object of that class is created.

 
